description: Deletes the access grant from the S3 Access Grants instance. You cannot undo an access grant deletion and the grantee will no longer have access to the S3 data. You must have the s3:DeleteAccessGrant permission to use this operation.

parameters.name: AccountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the S3 Access Grants instance.

parameters.name: AccessGrantId
parameters.description: The ID of the access grant. S3 Access Grants auto-generates this ID when you create the access grant.
